Package: apache-torblocker
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         apache2 (>= 2.4.0)
Description: Apache module for controlling access from Tor exit nodes
 Controls access from Tor exit nodes with three modes: block Tor
 traffic, allow only Tor traffic, or allow all. Automatically
 fetches and refreshes the Tor exit node list. Port of
 nginx-torblocker for Apache httpd. Written in Rust for memory safety.
